creator: BALEÀRIA EUROLINEAS MARÍTIMAS, S.A.
descriptionHtml:
Book your ideal travel in few seconds. With the Baleària app, this has never been so easy and comfortable.

Keep reading and discover all the advantages that the Baleària App has for you:

Travel to any Baleària destination
Check availability, rates and schedules in real time
Make your reservation in just one click
Enjoy all the benefits of being a Baleària Club member
All your bookings in a single device
Forget about queues! Access the boat directly with your Boarding Card
Receive offers, discounts and promotional codes
Pay easily and safely
Stay informed of all offers with our notifications

What are you waiting for? Download the app now and you can book and plan your trip at any time, quickly and safely!

At Baleària we care about your opinion to keep improving. Send us your suggestions to: soporte.app@balearia.com
descriptionShort: The easiest and most comfortable way to travel by ferry
